 Tower (Moscow)|One Tower]] ||{{flagicon|Russia}} [[Moscow]] || 405 ||  || 101 || 2024\n|-\n| [[Millennium Tower (Frankfurt)]] || {{flagicon|Germany}} [[Frankfurt]] || 369 || 1211 || 104 ||\n|-\n|[[Hermitage Plaza|Hermitage Plaza 1]]\n|{{Flagicon|France}} [[Paris]]\n|323\n|1060\n|92\n|2024\n|-Eiffel tower at 321 Metres\n|[[Hermitage Plaza|Hermitage Plaza 2]]\n|{{Flagicon|France}} [[Paris]]\n|323\n|1060\n|92\n|2024\n|-\n| [[Varso Tower]] ||{{flagicon|Poland}} [[Warsaw]] || 310 || 1017,06 || 54 || 2021\n|----> <!--\n| [[EGO Ofis Tower]] ||{{flagicon|Turkey}} [[Ankara]] || 301 || 988 || 66 || 2019  <ref>{{ctbuh | id = 26355| title = EGO Ofis Tower }}</ref> -->\n|-\n| [[Neva towers|Neva Towers]] 1<ref name=\"Neva Towers1\">{{cite web|url=http://www.nevatowers.ru/photo-report/|title=\u0425\u041e\u0414 \u0421\u0422\u0420\u041e\u0418\u0422\u0415\u041b\u042c\u0421\u0422\u0412\u0410}}</ref><ref name=\"Neva Towers2\">{{cite web|url=http://www.nevatowers.ru/uploads/documents/%D0%97%D0%B0%D0%BA%D0%BB%D1%8E%D1%87%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%B5%20%D0%9C%D0%93%D0%AD%20-3-2017%D0%B3.pdf|title=\u0414\u041e\u041a\u0423\u041c\u0415\u041d\u0422\u042b}}</ref>||{{flagicon|Russia}} [[Moscow]] || 302 || 990 || 68 || 2020\n|---> <!--\n|-\n| [[Grand Tower (Moscow)]] ||{{flagicon|Russia}} [[Moscow]] || 283.4 || 930 || 62 || 2021\n|- -->\n| [[22 Bishopsgate]] ||{{flagicon|United Kingdom}} [[London]] || 278 || 912 || 62 || 2019\n|-\n| Capital Towers 1<ref name=\"CapitalT\">{{cite web|url=http://capitaltowers.ru/|title=Capital Towers}}</ref> ||{{flagicon|Russia}} [[Moscow]] || 262.8 || 862 || 65 || 2020\n|-\n| Capital Towers 2<ref name=\"CapitalT\"/>||{{flagicon|Russia}} [[Moscow]] || 262.8 || 862 || 65 || 2020\n|-\n| Capital Towers 3<ref name=\"CapitalT\"/>||{{flagicon|Russia}} [[Moscow]] || 262.8 || 862 || 65 || 2020\n|---- >\n|-\n| Neskuchny Home & SPA<ref>{{cite web|url=http://neskuchny.gorn.ru/|title=\u041d\u0435\u0441\u043a\u0443\u0447\u043d\u044b\u0439 Home & SPA|access-date=9 April 2017|archive